title: I Got Better
lyrics: When we were over, it was overnight Light came on, it all felt right, when it all went wrong.

title: Love Somebody
lyrics: I just wanna love somebody Who won't leave a hole in my heart I just wanna love somebody That don't want me fallin' apart.

title: Interlude
lyrics: You're why I drink too much You're why I love that taste Yeah, if we're movin' on Girl, we just keep movin'.

title: Kiss Her In Front Of You
lyrics: But I can't wait to kiss her in front of you I can't wait to put you through the hell that you put me through.
